# PrimeAI — Private AI Workspace (Local RAG + Resume Analyzer)

PrimeAI is a private, local AI application that allows users to interact with their own documents using Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG). It also includes a Resume Analyzer and job matching features.

---

## 🚀 Features
- 📄 Upload documents and ask questions
- 🧠 RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation)
- 🧾 Resume Analyzer with ATS feedback
- 💼 Job matching mode
- ⚡ Fast local inference using Ollama
- 🔒 Fully private (runs locally)

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- Python
- LangChain
- ChromaDB
- Ollama
- Gradio
- PyPDF

---

